trans-unit.source: Enumerators provide read-only access to the data in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Enumeradores fornecem acesso somente leitura aos dados na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Enumerators cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: Enumeradores não podem ser usados para modificar a coleção subjacente.

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Inicialmente, o enumerador está posicionado antes do primeiro elemento na coleção.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Reset%2A> also brings the enumerator back to this position.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Reset%2A>também traz o enumerador de volta para essa posição.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Reset%2A>

trans-unit.source: At this position, calling <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Current%2A> throws an exception.
trans-unit.target: AT isso posicionar, chamando <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Current%2A>lança uma exceção.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Portanto, você deve chamar <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>para avançar o enumerador para o primeiro elemento da coleção antes de ler o valor de <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Current%2A>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ExtensionEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>
